title: Stop By Our Comfortable and Quiet Community Today!
posting_body: ['Welcome home!', 'Schedule a Tour!', 'Book an appointment online at 2tour.site/OHP/NJRF', 'New Orleans Court Apartments and Townhomes is conveniently located in Richfield close to restaurants, shopping, the airport, major highways, and the bus line.', 'Choose from our spacious 1- or 2-bedroom apartments, or 3-bedroom townhomes to find your perfect new home.', 'Enjoy our outdoor pool, playground, or picnic areas with grills.', 'We have controlled entries, on-site laundry, professional management and maintenance.', 'Cats are welcome and fiber-optic internet service is available! .', 'Visit today and see why you will love to call New Orleans Court home!', 'Home Amenities', 'Fiber-optic internet service available', 'Walk-in closet', 'Wall air conditioning', 'Balcony or patio options', 'Window coverings', 'Additional storage', 'Appliances in kitchen', 'Community Amenities', 'Pet friendly - some restrictions apply', 'Laundry facility', 'Outdoor swimming pool', 'Off street parking', 'Playground', 'BBQ & picnic area', '24 hour emergency maintenance', 'New Orleans Court Apartments Information', 'Address:', '50 W 78th St #101, Richfield MN, 55423', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Details/?pid=16', 'Deposit:', '$500', 'Application Fee:', '$45', 'Pet Fee:', '$100 (Note: Non-refundable)', 'Pet Deposit:', '$200 - 500', 'Office Hours', 'Monday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Tuesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Wednesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Thursday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Friday:', '9:00AM - 5:00PM', 'Saturday:', '11:00AM - 3:00PM', 'Sunday:', '12:00PM - 3:00PM']
